# 🧠 Emoji Predictor Web App

This is a fun and simple Machine Learning project that predicts an emoji based on your sentence. Built using **Python, Streamlit, and Scikit-learn**.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Predicts emojis like 😊 😢 😍 😡 🎉 💔 🐶
- Web-based interface using Streamlit
- Trained using TF-IDF + Logistic Regression
- Custom emoji dataset (CSV)

---

## 📂 Project Structure

emoji_predictor_project/
├── emoji_app.py # Streamlit app
├── emoji_dataset.csv # Custom training dataset
├── main.py # Console version (optional)
└── README.md # Project documentation


## 📦 Requirements

- Python 3.10 or above  
- Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install streamlit scikit-learn pandas

 Sample Dataset
The app uses a CSV file with two columns:

text: Sentence input

emoji: Matching emoji

Example:

csv
Copy
Edit
text,emoji
I am very happy today,😊
Feeling sad and alone,😢
I'm really angry now,😡
...

🧠 How it Works
Input sentence is vectorized using TfidfVectorizer

Trained on LogisticRegression

Predicts the closest matching emoji from the training data

Future Ideas
Use deep learning (like BERT) for better predictions

Allow multiple emojis

Deploy online using Streamlit Cloud

